# =============================================================================
# Copy to `.env.local` for: vercel dev   (loads these for /api/* routes)
# Production: Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# Never commit `.env` / `.env.local` with real secrets.
# =============================================================================

# ----- Anam AI avatar -----
# Persona UUID from https://lab.anam.ai (Widget tab). Allowlist your domain + Publish.
ANAM_PERSONA_ID=fa39aabd-ad5c-438f-b094-62bb8d818674

# Optional — server-only. GET /api/anam-session mints a session-token for the widget.
ANAM_API_KEY=46c74b48-1b50-4354-a2d5-be2f38a7c3a9

# =============================================================================
# Anam: "This agent is not authorized. Check your agent ID" (403 / 401)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1) Anam Lab → Widget → Allowed domains: add EXACTLY https://your-site.vercel.app
# 2) Temporarily try "Allow everywhere" to test.
# 3) Publish the persona. Redeploy Vercel after env changes.
# 4) Enable env vars for Production AND Preview if you use GitHub deploys.
# =============================================================================

# Not read by serverless routes — edit in the repo:
#   OpenWeather  → script.js CONFIG.weatherAPIKey
#   Google Maps  → index.html maps script URL
#   Firebase     → script.js firebaseConfig
